# Placeholder Images Directory

This directory contains example images for content demonstration.

## Recommended Placeholder Images:

- **hero-background.jpg** (1920x1080px) - Homepage hero section background
- **book-cover-1.jpg** through **book-cover-12.jpg** (400x600px) - Book cover examples
- **blog-featured-1.jpg** through **blog-featured-6.jpg** (1200x630px) - Blog post featured images
- **author-photo.jpg** (800x800px) - About page author photo
- **book-of-month.jpg** (400x600px) - Featured book of the month cover

All images should be optimized for web (under 500KB for photos, compressed JPG or WebP format).
